    "en": {
      "title": "A special meeting of party leaders will be held tomorrow in the Assembly",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special meeting of the Committee on Parliamentary Affairs will be held tomorrow (24) at 10:30 am to decide the future work of Parliament.",
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Dhammika Dasanayake said that all party leaders have been informed about this.",
        "It has already been decided to hold a debate on the government's decision to increase the electricity bill by 75 percent on the 29th Monday when the House is adjourned.",
        "In addition, the second reading debate on the Budget Appropriation Bill (Interim Budget), which has been submitted to the Parliament for the expenses of the next four months, will be held on the 30th, 31st of this month, and on the 1st and 2nd of next month.",
        "The Budget Appropriation Bill was presented to Parliament by Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena on the 9th."
      ],
